formulas.name: formula_BillingNextMonthCommonCharge
formulas.expression: IF (MONTH({!get_FifthSetConfirm.ContractStartDate__c})>{!get_FifthSetConfirm.NextMonthNumber__c}, TEXT(YEAR({!get_FifthSetConfirm.ContractStartDate__c})+1) & "年" & TEXT({!get_FifthSetConfirm.NextMonthNumber__c}) & "月分共益費", TEXT(YEAR({!get_FifthSetConfirm.ContractStartDate__c})) & "年" & TEXT({!get_FifthSetConfirm.NextMonthNumber__c}) & "月分共益費")

formulas.name: formula_BillingThisMonthCommonCharge
formulas.expression: IF ({!get_FifthSetConfirm.NextMonthNumber__c} = 1, TEXT(YEAR({!get_FifthSetConfirm.ContractStartDate__c})) & "年12月分共益費" , IF (MONTH({!get_FifthSetConfirm.ContractStartDate__c}) > {!get_FifthSetConfirm.NextMonthNumber__c}, TEXT(YEAR({!get_FifthSetConfirm.ContractStartDate__c})+1) & "年" & TEXT({!get_FifthSetConfirm.NextMonthNumber__c} -1) & "月分共益費", TEXT(YEAR({!get_FifthSetConfirm.ContractStartDate__c})) & "年" & TEXT({!get_FifthSetConfirm.NextMonthNumber__c} -1) & "月分共益費"))
